e of the incident electrons, the barrier\nheight and the thickness and number of barriers. We show that the matrix\ndeterminant can be used as a test of the numerical accuracy in real\ncalculations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 Dec 2015 20:11:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-04-20"}
