r flow at radii larger than\nthe innermost stable circular orbit, as predicted by the Lense-Thirring QPO\nmodels.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 9 Dec 2015 02:53:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 10 Mar 2016 07:04:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-03-23"}
