ices may follow rotation of the polarizing magnetic field, is found\ntoo.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 9 Dec 2015 13:41:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 29 Jan 2016 05:06:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-02-24"}
